ORFTEXT000041755949"> Texte suivant <span class="fleche">  &rsaquo;</span></a></li></div><div class="precedent-suivant-list-right"></div></ul></nav></div></div><div class="modal fade" id="modal-timeline" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-label="Chronologie des versions de l’article" aria-hidden="true"><div class="modal-dialog chronolegi timeline-modal" role="document"><div class="modal-content"><div class="print-page" role="presentation"><div class="modal-header"><button class="btn-inverse btn-close" type="button" data-dismiss="modal" title="Fermer" aria-describedby="Chronolegi"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span><span class="sr-only">Fermer</span></button><div class="title-popin title-popin-div" id="Chronolegi">
